Cyber Claw:




Cyber Claw hovered in the air, watching as the battle deminished. She 
growled as she watched it happen. She couldn't let the attackers escape 
without having one of them answer her. The two Predacons she spoke with were 
no use to her, since they knew nothing about Megatron, even spouting any lie 
about him.

She flew closer to the center of the conflict, and hovered above a bot 
calling into his comm-link to the Maximals. It was Zardus, and he looked 
promising. He seemed to be the one that was in charge of the attack.

She lowered down to the flier until she was behind him. "Hey you!" she 
snapped at him. She prepared herself just in case he fired. Megatron may 
have told him about her.


(Just a note before someone barks at me: Cyb doesn't know the Alliance 
members aren't Predacons.)
